HEADWORD: kissing kin
<hw>kiss"ing kin`</hw>. <def>Any relative more distant than the
immediate family, sufficiently well acquainted to be greeted with a
kiss, such as a <er>kissing cousin</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

